Entry.JapaneseText: どれが本物のミリッツァなんだよ……！ ああ、頭がクラクラしやがるぜ……
Entry.EnglishText: Which one is the real Militsa?! Ugh, this is making my head spin...

Entry.JapaneseText: しっかりしろ、<Tytree>。 そうやって混乱すれば、相手の思うツボだ。
Entry.EnglishText: Get it together, <Tytree>. If you let yourself get confused, you'll play right into her hands!
